casebody.data:
No. 10-7900. Robert Breest, Petitioner v. New Hampshire. 562 U.S. 1197, 131 S. Ct. 1055,

178 L. Ed. 2d 860,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 921. January 24, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of New Hampshire dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
